snippet.title: Triad - apple ][
snippet.description:
YUIHJKNMfor moving with diagonals. F for fire.

It's basically TicTacToe with a twist. Every square contains an opponent and each of them is defeated by different strategy.
Disk image is available in the Asimov archives.
